Mauritius Gambling Revenue to Rise 17% in 2011, l’Express Says

-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 
2011-04-25T06:34:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-25/mauritius-gambling-revenue-to-rise-17-in-2011-l-express-says.html
Mauritius’s fiscal revenue from
gambling is expected to grow by 17 percent to 1.7 billion rupees
in 2011 compared with a year earlier, Port Louis-based l’Express
newspaper cited Sudhamo Lal, the director-general of the
Mauritius Revenue Authority, as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story: Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port
Louis via Johannesburg at 
 gbell16@bloomberg.net  